From David Engel Subject Re Wanted Opinions on MAG and NANAO monitor sleeping dragon wrote I'm looking to buy a monitor soon and it seems that I can't decide what monitor I should I have a MAG this is a dpi version and it using a TRINITON tube and a NANAO in Good luck finding an When I was looking around back in December January Mag wasn't producing any because they couldn't get tubes from I asked when they expected to restart production as I was willing to wait a few months to get an but they said not any time I wound up getting a and am extremely happy with David David Engel Optical Data Systems Arapaho Road Richardson TX